name: ~ The Star Pharaoh - Part II ~
description:
Their ruler, Menes, and his petty sycophants of court - the lay priests, aristocrats, and haughty scribes - all crumple beneath the glory that fills the twinkling night sky. The Star Pharaoh descends, the skyline itself funneling down into humanoid form. It is graced by the Ankh, the Eye of Horus, and the rearing cobra Uraeus, as foretold by the Sem-Priest of Ptah. Proceeding along the alleys and down passageways, reality shimmers, warping and inverting as it passes. The people flee. But not the artisan. As the land groans and the rocks tumble to seal her in darkness, she continues the Work.
